<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1037838" n="1"/> 
    <opener><salute><lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-140736662">F. C.</rs> Amico suo <abbr>pl.</abbr> colendo <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">N. B.</rs></salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Merito tibi, <choice><orig><g ref="#ohat">ô</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> amice succenserem, quod me in singulis tuis <rs type="letter">literis</rs>, ad quarum lectionem me
<lb/>non solum lachr<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>mas effundere, sed plane obmutescere et obstupescere necesse est, i<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>erita laude
<lb/>pene obruis, nisi qualem me esse deceat, et quantus sit affectus erga me tuus, ex iisdem di<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>dicissem; ah parce qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so inposterum tam mollibus verbis, et cogita me tanta eloquentia
<lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ditum non esse, ut tibi pro merito respondere, aut amorem tuum satis dignis encomiis ce<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>lebrare queam; sufficit mihi, quod Deo gratias agere possum, quod me in cognitionem virtu<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tum tuarum, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sane unice me permoverunt, ut amicitiam tuam expetiverim, deducere
<lb/>dignatus fuerit: sufficit mihi, quod eundem Deum <abbr>O. M.</abbr> supplex oro, ut velit amiciti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> no<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>str<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> benedicere et clementer concedere, ut ambo fructus ejus utilissimos non semel sed s<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>pi<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>us sentiamus. Amemus erga nos invicem sincere, et amorem nostrum non verbis <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>quid enim
<lb/>verbis opus inter eos, qui se invicem bene norunt?<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> sed operibus comprobemus. Scripsi tibi
<lb/>in prioribus meis <rs type="letter">literis</rs> me post <date>Pascha</date> <rs type="place">Basileam</rs> venturum esse, sed ignosce quod te inani spe
<lb/>lactavi; obediendum est voluntati <rs type="person">Parentum</rs>, qui ut per <rs type="place">Genevam</rs> et <rs type="place">Lugdunum</rs> iter fa<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>ciam et <rs type="place">Parisios</rs> me conferam volunt, proficiscar itaque <date>post duas septimanas</date> aut citius,
<lb/>si se occasio obtulerit; <rs type="place">Genev<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> per aliquot hebdomadas aut forte diutius co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>orabor, ubi me
<lb/>cum <rs type="person">amico</rs> nostro co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>uni, quem <rs type="place">Bern<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> frustra expectabam, plus quam semel exhilarabo.
<lb/>Te autem, <choice><orig><g ref="#ohat">ô</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> optime, quando iterum videbo, tuoque consortio fruar? ah metuo valde, ne fo<unclear reason="lost"><gap/></unclear>
<lb/>nos diu nimis divellat, spem tamen foveo <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> si me falleret, dolore penitus conficerer<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice>
<lb/>me vel <rs type="place">domum</rs> rediturum, antequam tu abeas, vel forte tamdiu <rs type="place">Genev<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> mansurum, donec
<lb/>tu quoque illuc veneris; patienter itaque ferendum et expectandum, quid Deus in nos decre<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>verit. <abbr>Dnum</abbr> <rs type="person">Waldkirch</rs> ad Professionem Juridicam frustra hic aspirasse, verissimum est, re<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>dibit ille hac <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>state <rs type="place">Basileam</rs>, nec ullam sibi spem faciet eam adhuc obtinendi, quia
<lb/>ejusmodi hominem qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>runt <rs type="person">Bernates</rs>, qualem (ut credo) in toto terrarum orbe vix inve<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>nient, adeo ut hanc et alias ob rationes valde metuendum sit, ne illorum, qui Professio<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>nem Juridicam hic erigere volunt, irritus sit conatus. Ille quidam, <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quo audivisti me
<lb/>quoque spe hac animum lactasse, sine dubio est <rs type="person">Paravicinus</rs>, qui in <rs type="letter">literis</rs> quas mihi 
<pb facs="1037839" n="2"/> 
<lb/>dedit <choice><sic>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endaditiis</sic><corr>commendatitiis</corr></choice> idem <rs type="person">Pastori</rs> cuidam, qui mihi <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>legit, expresse scripsit, licet
<lb/><rs type="person">privignum</rs><note type="comment">Privignum bedeutet Stiefsohn.</note> ejus, ne hoc faceret, rogaverim, ipsique non hanc sed aliam abitus mei causam
<lb/>esse candide aperuerim; quod me quam male habuerit ipsi data occasione indicare poteris,
<lb/>et simul ab eo sciscitari, quisnam ipsi suggesserit, me hanc ob causam <rs type="place">Bernam</rs> profectum
  <lb/>esse. Deploro miseram sortem, quam sortita est <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-122123158">Grundleri</rs> <rs type="biblio">Disputatio</rs>, et illam tam se<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>vero <rs type="person">censore</rs> opus habuisse <del/>doleo. <abbr>Dnum</abbr> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089640587">Graffenried</rs> majoris libertatis et consor<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tii gratia ad <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-129684406">Platerum</rs> transiisse jam ante <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="person">Patruo</rs> meo audivi. Quem per <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">...</rs>
<lb/>intellexerim, recte conjecisti, male autem egisti dum illum veterem meum <rs type="person">amicum</rs> no<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>minasti, neminem enim nisi tui similem pro amico agnoscere, imo tibi soli amici no<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>men jure tribuere et l<unclear reason="illegible"><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>t</unclear>o animo acclamare possum:</p> <closer>Vale, mi amice, et amico tuo in<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tegerrimo fave. <dateline>Datum in tenebris <rs type="place">Hindelbanckianis</rs> <abbr>a. d.</abbr> <date when="1710-04-19">19. Aprilis 1710</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div>
